<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>삼일 커피챗 챌린지</title>
<style>
@import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard@v1.3.9/dist/web/static/pretendard.css');

:root{
  --bg:#FBF6F0;
  --surface:#FFFFFF;
  --surface-2:#FFFBF7;
  --ink:#2A231D;
  --ink-soft:#7A6F64;
  --ink-faint:#A99D90;
  --brand:#EE5836;
  --brand-deep:#D33E1E;
  --brand-soft:#FFE9E1;
  --courage:#F2A93B;
  --courage-soft:#FFF1DB;
  --go:#1FA266;
  --go-soft:#E4F5EC;
  --line:#EFE6DB;
  --line-soft:#F5EEE5;
  --shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(42,35,29,.04), 0 8px 24px rgba(42,35,29,.06);
  --shadow-lg:0 12px 40px rgba(42,35,29,.12);
  --r:18px;
  --font:'Pretendard','Noto Sans CJK KR','Noto Sans KR',-apple-system,system-ui,sans-serif;
}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
html,body{height:100%}
body{
  font-family:var(--font);
  background:var(--bg);
  color:var(--ink);
  -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
  text-rendering:optimizeLegibility;
  letter-spacing:-.01em;
}
button{font-family:inherit;cursor:pointer;border:none;background:none;color:inherit}
::-webkit-scrollbar{width:9px;height:9px}
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:#E4D9CC;border-radius:9px;border:2px solid var(--bg)}

/* ============ APP SHELL ============ */
.app{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:248px 1fr;
  height:100vh;
  min-height:680px;
}

/* ---- Sidebar ---- */
.side{
  background:linear-gradient(180deg,#fff 0%,#FFFBF7 100%);
  border-right:1px solid var(--line);
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  padding:22px 18px;
}
.brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:6px 8px 22px}
.brand-mark{
  width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:11px;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--brand) 0%,#FF8A4D 100%);
  display:grid;place-items:center;flex:none;
  box-shadow:0 6px 14px rgba(238,88,54,.32);
  position:relative;
}
.brand-mark svg{width:21px;height:21px}
.brand-name{font-weight:800;font-size:15px;line-height:1.15;letter-spacing:-.02em}
.brand-name small{display:block;font-weight:600;font-size:10.5px;color:var(--ink-faint);letter-spacing:.04em;margin-top:2px}

.nav{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:3px;margin-top:4px}
.nav-label{font-size:10.5px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink-faint);letter-spacing:.08em;padding:6px 10px 8px}
.nav-item{
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:11px;
  padding:11px 12px;border-radius:12px;
  font-size:13.5px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink-soft);
  transition:.16s;position:relative;text-align:left;width:100%;
}
.nav-item svg{width:18px;height:18px;flex:none;opacity:.85}
.nav-item:hover{background:var(--line-soft);color:var(--ink)}
.nav-item.on{background:var(--brand-soft);color:var(--brand-deep)}
.nav-item.on svg{opacity:1}
.nav-item .badge{
  margin-left:auto;background:var(--brand);color:#fff;font-size:10px;font-weight:800;
  min-width:18px;height:18px;border-radius:9px;display:grid;place-items:center;padding:0 5px;
}

.side-foot{margin-top:auto}
.courage-card{
  background:linear-gradient(150deg,#FFF7EC 0%,#FFEFD8 100%);
  border:1px solid #FBE6C4;border-radius:16px;padding:14px 15px;
}
.courage-top{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:9px}
.courage-lab{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:11.5px;font-weight:700;color:#B07A1C}
.courage-lvl{font-size:10px;font-weight:800;color:#fff;background:var(--courage);padding:3px 8px;border-radius:20px}
.courage-pts{font-size:25px;font-weight:800;color:#9A6912;line-height:1;letter-spacing:-.03em}
.courage-pts span{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#C79A4E;margin-left:3px}
.gauge{height:7px;background:#F6E1BC;border-radius:6px;margin-top:11px;overflow:hidden}
.gauge-fill{height:100%;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--courage),#FFC766);border-radius:6px;transition:width .7s cubic-bezier(.2,.8,.2,1)}
.courage-next{font-size:10.5px;color:#B7873A;margin-top:7px;font-weight:600}

/* ---- Main ---- */
.main{overflow-y:auto;position:relative}
.topbar{
  position:sticky;top:0;z-index:20;
  background:rgba(251,246,240,.82);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
  padding:17px 30px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;
}
.topbar h1{font-size:18px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.02em}
.topbar .sub{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-soft);font-weight:500;margin-top:2px}
.me{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px}
.me-av{width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#5C6BC0,#7E8DE0);display:grid;place-items:center;color:#fff;font-weight:800;font-size:13px}
.me-txt{font-size:12.5px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.2}
.me-txt small{display:block;font-weight:500;color:var(--ink-faint);font-size:10.5px}

.view{padding:26px 30px 60px}

/* ============ DISCOVER (신청하기) ============ */
.discover{display:grid;grid-template-columns:minmax(0,1fr) 312px;gap:24px;max-width:980px;margin:0 auto}
.swipe-wrap{position:relative}
.deck-hint{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:14px}
.deck-hint .t{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink-soft)}
.deck-hint .ai-pill{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;font-size:11px;font-weight:800;color:var(--brand-deep);background:var(--brand-soft);padding:5px 11px;border-radius:30px}
.deck-hint .ai-pill svg{width:13px;height:13px}

.card{
  background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:24px;
  box-shadow:var(--shadow);overflow:hidden;position:relative;
  animation:cardin .45s cubic-bezier(.2,.85,.25,1);
}
@keyframes cardin{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(14px) scale(.98)}to{opacity:1;transform:none}}
.card-banner{height:96px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.card-banner .blob{position:absolute;border-radius:50%;filter:blur(2px);opacity:.9}
.card-rating{position:absolute;top:13px;right:14px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.92);backdrop-filter:blur(4px);
  padding:5px 11px;border-radius:30px;font-size:12px;font-weight:800;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;box-shadow:0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.08)}
.card-rating .star{color:var(--courage)}
.card-head{padding:0 22px;margin-top:-34px;position:relative;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;gap:14px}
.av-lg{width:74px;height:74px;border-radius:20px;display:grid;place-items:center;color:#fff;font-weight:800;font-size:27px;
  border:3px solid #fff;box-shadow:0 8px 20px rgba(42,35,29,.16);flex:none}
.head-meta{padding-bottom:5px}
.head-meta .nm{font-size:20px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.02em;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.head-meta .nm .lvl-tag{font-size:10px;font-weight:800;color:#7A5AB5;background:#EFE9FB;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:20px}
.head-meta .rl{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--ink-soft);font-weight:600;margin-top:3px}
.tags{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:6px;padding:16px 22px 4px}
.tag{font-size:11.5px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink-soft);background:var(--line-soft);border:1px solid var(--line);padding:5px 11px;border-radius:9px}
.tag.hot{color:var(--brand-deep);background:var(--brand-soft);border-color:#FBD5C8}
.bio{padding:12px 22px 4px;font-size:13.5px;line-height:1.7;color:#5C5248}
.bio b{color:var(--ink);font-weight:700}

.ai-topics{margin:16px 22px 0;background:linear-gradient(160deg,#FFF9F2,#FFF4E9);border:1px solid #FBE7CF;border-radius:16px;padding:15px 16px}
.ai-topics .h{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:11px}
.ai-topics .h .l{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:800;color:#B27A1A}
.ai-topics .h .l svg{width:15px;height:15px}
.regen{font-size:10.5px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink-faint);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;padding:4px 8px;border-radius:8px;transition:.15s}
.regen:hover{background:#FBEAD2;color:#B27A1A}
.regen svg{width:12px;height:12px}
.topic{display:flex;gap:10px;padding:8px 0;font-size:13px;line-height:1.5;color:#5C5248;border-top:1px dashed #F1DEC2}
.topic:first-of-type{border-top:none;padding-top:2px}
.topic .n{flex:none;width:19px;height:19px;border-radius:7px;background:#fff;border:1px solid #F0DCBE;color:#C68A2A;font-size:11px;font-weight:800;display:grid;place-items:center;margin-top:1px}
.topic b{color:var(--ink);font-weight:700}

.card-foot{padding:18px 22px 22px}
.tmpl-lab{font-size:11.5px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-bottom:9px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
.tmpl-row{display:flex;gap:7px;margin-bottom:13px}
.tmpl{flex:1;padding:9px 6px;border-radius:11px;border:1.5px solid var(--line);background:#fff;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink-soft);transition:.15s;text-align:center}
.tmpl:hover{border-color:#E7C9BE}
.tmpl.on{border-color:var(--brand);background:var(--brand-soft);color:var(--brand-deep)}
.msg-preview{background:var(--surface-2);border:1px solid var(--line);border-left:3px solid var(--brand);border-radius:0 12px 12px 0;
  padding:13px 15px;font-size:12.5px;line-height:1.65;color:#5C5248;margin-bottom:16px;min-height:64px;white-space:pre-line}
.msg-preview .seg{transition:.3s}
.act-row{display:flex;gap:11px}
.btn{border-radius:14px;font-weight:800;font-size:14px;transition:.16s;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:8px}
.btn-pass{flex:none;width:54px;height:54px;border-radius:15px;border:1.5px solid var(--line);background:#fff;color:var(--ink-faint)}
.btn-pass:hover{border-color:#E0CFC1;color:var(--ink-soft);background:var(--surface-2)}
.btn-pass svg{width:22px;height:22px}
.btn-apply{flex:1;height:54px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--go),#27B978);color:#fff;box-shadow:0 8px 20px rgba(31,162,102,.3)}
.btn-apply:hover{transform:translateY(-1px);box-shadow:0 12px 26px rgba(31,162,102,.38)}
.btn-apply:active{transform:translateY(0)}
.btn-apply svg{width:19px;height:19px}

/* side rail */
.rail{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px}
.panel{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--r);box-shadow:var(--shadow);overflow:hidden}
.panel-h{padding:15px 17px 0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between}
.panel-h .t{font-size:13.5px;font-weight:800;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px}
.panel-h .t svg{width:16px;height:16px;color:var(--brand)}
.panel-h .more{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink-faint)}

.lb-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:11px;padding:11px 17px;border-top:1px solid var(--line-soft)}
.lb-row:first-of-type{border-top:none}
.lb-row.me{background:var(--brand-soft)}
.rank{width:24px;height:24px;border-radius:8px;display:grid;place-items:center;font-size:12px;font-weight:800;flex:none}
.rank.r1{background:#FFF3D4;color:#C99A1E}.rank.r2{background:#EEF1F4;color:#8B97A4}.rank.r3{background:#F8E8DC;color:#C07A4A}
.rank.rx{background:var(--line-soft);color:var(--ink-faint)}
.lb-av{width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:9px;display:grid;place-items:center;color:#fff;font-weight:800;font-size:12px;flex:none}
.lb-info{flex:1;min-width:0}
.lb-info .n{font-size:12.5px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.2}
.lb-info .s{font-size:10.5px;color:var(--ink-faint);font-weight:600;margin-top:1px}
.lb-pt{font-size:13px;font-weight:800;color:var(--courage)}

.tip{padding:14px 17px}
.tip .row{display:flex;gap:10px;padding:7px 0;font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;color:var(--ink-soft)}
.tip .row svg{width:15px;height:15px;flex:none;margin-top:1px;color:var(--go)}
.tip b{color:var(--ink);font-weight:700}

.streak{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:13px;padding:15px 17px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#FFF6EC,#FFEEDC)}
.streak .ico{width:42px;height:42px;border-radius:13px;background:#fff;display:grid;place-items:center;font-size:22px;box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(242,169,59,.22)}
.streak .x .n{font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:#9A6912}
.streak .x .s{font-size:11px;color:#BC8A3D;font-weight:600}

/* ============ generic section pages ============ */
.page-wrap{max-width:980px;margin:0 auto}
.kpi-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:14px;margin-bottom:24px}
.kpi{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:16px;padding:17px 18px;box-shadow:var(--shadow)}
.kpi .ic{width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:11px;display:grid;place-items:center;margin-bottom:12px}
.kpi .v{font-size:26px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.03em;line-height:1}
.kpi .l{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-soft);font-weight:600;margin-top:6px}
.kpi .d{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;margin-top:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:3px}
.kpi .d.up{color:var(--go)}

/* schedule */
.sched-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 320px;gap:22px}
.cal{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--r);box-shadow:var(--shadow);padding:20px}
.cal-h{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:16px}
.cal-h .m{font-size:16px;font-weight:800}
.cal-nav{display:flex;gap:6px}
.cal-nav button{width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:9px;border:1px solid var(--line);display:grid;place-items:center;color:var(--ink-soft)}
.cal-nav button:hover{background:var(--line-soft)}
.dow{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(7,1fr);gap:5px;margin-bottom:7px}
.dow span{text-align:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink-faint);padding:4px 0}
.days{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(7,1fr);gap:5px}
.day{aspect-ratio:1;border-radius:11px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:flex-start;padding-top:7px;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink-soft);position:relative;border:1px solid transparent}
.day.mut{color:var(--ink-faint);opacity:.45}
.day.today{background:var(--brand-soft);color:var(--brand-deep);font-weight:800;border-color:#FBD5C8}
.day .dot{width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;margin-top:4px}
.day .dot.go{background:var(--go)}.day .dot.wait{background:var(--courage)}
.day.has{cursor:pointer}.day.has:hover{background:var(--line-soft)}

.up-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:11px}
.up-item{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:15px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);padding:14px 15px;display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.up-item .bar{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;bottom:0;width:4px}
.up-item .av{width:42px;height:42px;border-radius:12px;display:grid;place-items:center;color:#fff;font-weight:800;font-size:15px;flex:none}
.up-item .x{flex:1;min-width:0}
.up-item .x .n{font-size:13.5px;font-weight:800}
.up-item .x .s{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--ink-soft);font-weight:600;margin-top:3px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.up-item .when{text-align:right;flex:none}
.up-item .when .d{font-size:12px;font-weight:800;color:var(--brand-deep)}
.up-item .when .t{font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-faint);font-weight:600;margin-top:2px}
.st{font-size:10px;font-weight:800;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:20px}
.st.go{background:var(--go-soft);color:#15784A}
.st.wait{background:var(--courage-soft);color:#B07A1C}

/* network map */
.netbox{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--r);box-shadow:var(--shadow);overflow:hidden;position:relative}
.net-head{padding:18px 22px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line-soft);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between}
.net-head .t{font-size:15px;font-weight:800}
.net-head .lg{display:flex;gap:14px}
.net-head .lg span{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink-soft);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px}
.net-head .lg i{width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block}
.net-svg{display:block;width:100%;background:radial-gradient(circle at 50% 45%,#FFFBF6,#FBF4EC)}

/* requests / 신청 현황 */
.req-card{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--r);box-shadow:var(--shadow);overflow:hidden}
.req-head{padding:18px 22px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line-soft);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between}
.req-head .t{font-size:15px;font-weight:800}
.req-head .lg{display:flex;gap:14px}
.req-head .lg span{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink-soft);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px}
.req-head .lg i{width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block}
.req-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;padding:15px 22px;border-top:1px solid var(--line-soft)}
.req-row:first-child{border-top:none}
.req-row .av{width:42px;height:42px;border-radius:12px;display:grid;place-items:center;color:#fff;font-weight:800;font-size:15px;flex:none}
.req-row .x{flex:1;min-width:0}
.req-row .x .n{font-size:14px;font-weight:800;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.req-row .x .n .when{font-size:10.5px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink-faint)}
.req-row .x .s{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--ink-soft);font-weight:600;margin-top:3px}
.req-detail{text-align:right;flex:none;max-width:46%}
.req-detail .d{font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-faint);font-weight:600;margin-top:5px}
.req-st{font-size:10.5px;font-weight:800;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:20px;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
.req-st.wait{background:var(--courage-soft);color:#B07A1C}
.req-st.go{background:var(--go-soft);color:#15784A}
.req-st.dec{background:var(--line-soft);color:var(--ink-soft)}
.req-st .pulse{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:#F2A93B;display:inline-block;animation:pulse 1.4s ease-in-out infinite}
@keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:.35;transform:scale(.8)}50%{opacity:1;transform:scale(1.15)}}
.req-row.fresh{background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--brand-soft),transparent);animation:freshin .5s ease}
@keyframes freshin{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(-6px)}to{opacity:1;transform:none}}
.reset-btn{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:6px;width:100%;margin-top:12px;padding:8px;border-radius:11px;border:1px solid var(--line);background:#fff;color:var(--ink-faint);font-size:11.5px;font-weight:700;transition:.15s}
.reset-btn svg{width:14px;height:14px}
.reset-btn:hover{color:var(--ink-soft);background:var(--surface-2);border-color:#E0CFC1}
.save-hint{text-align:center;font-size:10px;color:var(--ink-faint);font-weight:600;margin-top:8px;opacity:.85}

/* topbar right: bell + notif */
.topbar-right{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;position:relative}
.bell{position:relative;width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:12px;background:var(--surface-2);border:1px solid var(--line);display:grid;place-items:center;color:var(--ink-soft)}
.bell:hover{background:#fff}
.bell svg{width:20px;height:20px}
.bell-dot{position:absolute;top:8px;right:9px;width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--brand);border:2px solid #fff}
.notif-panel{position:absolute;top:54px;right:0;width:340px;max-height:70vh;overflow:auto;background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:16px;box-shadow:0 18px 48px rgba(70,50,35,.18);z-index:60}
.notif-head{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:14px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line-soft);font-weight:800;font-size:13px}
.notif-head button{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--brand-deep);background:none}
.notif-item{padding:13px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line-soft);display:flex;gap:10px}
.notif-item:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.notif-item.unread{background:var(--brand-soft)}
.notif-item .nt{font-size:12.5px;font-weight:800;color:var(--ink)}
.notif-item .nb{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-top:3px;line-height:1.45}
.notif-item .nx{font-size:10px;color:var(--ink-faint);margin-top:4px}
.notif-empty{padding:30px;text-align:center;color:var(--ink-faint);font-size:12px}

/* login */
/* ===================== SEND ANIMATION (용기 불꽃 + 편지) ===================== */
.send-anim{position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:140;display:grid;place-items:center;background:radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(255,238,228,.93), rgba(251,246,240,.97));animation:saIn .2s ease}
.send-anim.out{animation:saOut .26s ease forwards}
@keyframes saIn{from{opacity:0}to{opacity:1}}
@keyframes saOut{to{opacity:0}}
.send-stage{position:relative;width:260px;height:260px;display:grid;place-items:center}
.send-anim .ring{position:absolute;width:92px;height:92px;border-radius:50%;border:3px solid var(--brand);animation:ringBurst 1.1s ease-out forwards}
@keyframes ringBurst{0%{transform:scale(.3);opacity:.7}100%{transform:scale(2.7);opacity:0}}
.send-anim .flame{position:absolute;font-size:56px;animation:flameP .5s ease-in-out infinite alternate;filter:drop-shadow(0 6px 14px rgba(238,88,54,.45))}
@keyframes flameP{from{transform:scale(.9) translateY(3px)}to{transform:scale(1.14) translateY(-3px)}}
.send-anim .letter{position:absolute;font-size:62px;animation:letterFly 1.25s cubic-bezier(.5,-.2,.3,1) forwards;filter:drop-shadow(0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.18))}
@keyframes letterFly{
  0%{transform:translate(0,22px) scale(.4) rotate(-8deg);opacity:0}
  22%{transform:translate(0,0) scale(1.06) rotate(0);opacity:1}
  55%{transform:translate(22px,-34px) scale(1) rotate(7deg);opacity:1}
  100%{transform:translate(186px,-282px) scale(.24) rotate(24deg);opacity:0}}
.send-anim .spark{position:absolute;width:11px;height:11px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--courage),var(--brand));opacity:0;animation:sparkOut .82s ease-out forwards}
@keyframes sparkOut{0%{transform:translate(0,0) scale(.4);opacity:1}100%{transform:translate(var(--tx),var(--ty)) scale(.2);opacity:0}}
.send-anim .plus{position:absolute;top:32%;font-weight:900;color:var(--go);font-size:21px;opacity:0;animation:plusUp 1.15s ease-out .35s forwards;text-shadow:0 2px 7px rgba(255,255,255,.85)}
@keyframes plusUp{0%{transform:translateY(12px);opacity:0}30%{opacity:1}100%{transform:translateY(-44px);opacity:0}}
.send-cap{position:absolute;bottom:22%;font-weight:800;color:var(--brand-deep);font-size:17px}

/* ===================== TESTIMONIALS (우수 연결 후기) ===================== */
.testi{padding:2px}
.t-pair{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
.t-av{width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:10px;display:grid;place-items:center;color:#fff;font-weight:800;font-size:13px;flex:none}
.t-arrow{width:16px;height:16px;color:var(--ink-faint);flex:none}
.t-names{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink);margin-left:4px;line-height:1.25}
.t-names b{font-weight:800}
.t-dept{font-size:10.5px;color:var(--ink-faint);font-weight:600;margin-top:1px}
.t-topic{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:8px;margin-top:10px;font-size:11.5px;font-weight:800;color:var(--brand-deep);background:var(--brand-soft);padding:6px 10px;border-radius:9px}
.t-stars{color:var(--courage);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:1px;flex:none}
.t-quote{margin-top:9px;font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--ink-soft)}
.t-empty{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-faint);padding:10px}
.panel-h .more{cursor:pointer}

/* ===================== INCOMING PEER REQUESTS ===================== */
.incoming-card{border:1.5px solid #DCE0F5}
.inbadge{display:inline-block;min-width:20px;height:20px;line-height:20px;text-align:center;background:#5C6BC0;color:#fff;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;font-weight:800;padding:0 6px;margin-left:6px}
.req-head .lg.muted{font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-faint);font-weight:600}
.in-row .s{font-style:italic;color:var(--ink-soft)}
.in-actions{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-left:auto;flex:none}
.in-actions button{font-size:12.5px;font-weight:800;padding:8px 16px;border-radius:11px;border:none;cursor:pointer;transition:.15s}
.in-acc{background:var(--go);color:#fff}
.in-acc:hover{background:#178a55}
.in-dec{background:var(--surface-2);color:var(--ink-soft);border:1px solid var(--line)!important}
.in-dec:hover{background:var(--line-soft)}

.login-scrim{position:fixed;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#FBF1E8,#F6E7DA);display:grid;place-items:center;z-index:100;padding:20px}
.login-card{width:min(440px,94vw);background:var(--surface);border-radius:24px;box-shadow:0 30px 80px rgba(80,55,35,.22);padding:30px 30px 24px}
.login-brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:13px;margin-bottom:16px}
.login-brand .lb-t{font-size:18px;font-weight:800}
.login-brand .lb-s{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-soft);font-weight:600}
.login-lead{font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-soft);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:20px}
.fld{display:block;margin-bottom:13px}
.fld>span{display:block;font-size:11.5px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-bottom:6px}
.fld input,.fld select{width:100%;height:46px;border:1.5px solid var(--line);border-radius:13px;padding:0 14px;font-size:14px;font-family:inherit;background:#fff;color:var(--ink)}
.fld input:focus,.fld select:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--brand)}
.fld-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px}
.login-btn{width:100%;height:50px;border-radius:14px;background:var(--brand);color:#fff;font-weight:800;font-size:15px;margin-top:10px;transition:.15s}
.login-btn:hover{background:var(--brand-deep)}
.login-err{color:#D8472E;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;text-align:center;margin-top:10px;min-height:16px}
.login-foot{text-align:center;font-size:11.5px;color:var(--ink-faint);margin-top:14px}
.login-foot a{color:var(--brand-deep);font-weight:700}
.app{display:none}
body.authed .app{display:flex}
body.authed .login-scrim{display:none}

/* leaderboard full */
.lead-head{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#FFF7EC,#FFEEDB);border:1px solid #FBE6C4;border-radius:var(--r);padding:22px 24px;margin-bottom:20px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:20px}
.podium{display:flex;align-items:flex-end;gap:14px;flex:none}
.pod{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:7px}
.pod .av{border-radius:14px;display:grid;place-items:center;color:#fff;font-weight:800;border:3px solid #fff;box-shadow:var(--shadow)}
.pod.first .av{width:60px;height:60px;font-size:20px}
.pod.side .av{width:48px;height:48px;font-size:16px}
.pod .nm{font-size:12px;font-weight:800}
.pod .pt{font-size:11px;font-weight:800;color:var(--courage)}
.pod .crown{font-size:18px;margin-bottom:-4px}
.lead-copy{flex:1}
.lead-copy h3{font-size:17px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:6px}
.lead-copy p{font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-soft);line-height:1.6;font-weight:500}
.lead-table{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--r);box-shadow:var(--shadow);overflow:hidden}
.lt-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;padding:14px 20px;border-top:1px solid var(--line-soft)}
.lt-row:first-child{border-top:none}
.lt-row.me{background:var(--brand-soft)}
.lt-row .badges{display:flex;gap:5px;margin-left:auto}
.lt-row .bdg{font-size:15px}
.lt-row .pt{font-size:16px;font-weight:800;color:var(--courage);width:60px;text-align:right}
.lt-row .av{width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:11px;display:grid;place-items:center;color:#fff;font-weight:800;font-size:14px;flex:none}
.lt-row .info .n{font-size:14px;font-weight:800}
.lt-row .info .s{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--ink-faint);font-weight:600;margin-top:2px}

/* ============ TOAST / RESULT MODAL ============ */
.scrim{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(42,35,29,.4);backdrop-filter:blur(3px);z-index:90;display:grid;place-items:center;opacity:0;pointer-events:none;transition:.25s}
.scrim.show{opacity:1;pointer-events:auto}
.result{background:#fff;border-radius:26px;width:380px;max-width:90vw;padding:32px 30px 26px;text-align:center;box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg);transform:scale(.92);transition:.3s cubic-bezier(.2,.9,.3,1.1)}
.scrim.show .result{transform:scale(1)}
.result .burst{width:88px;height:88px;border-radius:26px;margin:0 auto 18px;display:grid;place-items:center;font-size:42px;position:relative}
.result h2{font-size:21px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.02em;margin-bottom:8px}
.result p{font-size:13.5px;color:var(--ink-soft);line-height:1.6;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:20px}
.result p b{color:var(--ink)}
.pts-gain{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;background:var(--courage-soft);border:1px solid #FBE2BC;border-radius:30px;padding:8px 16px;margin-bottom:22px;font-weight:800;color:#B07A1C;font-size:14px}
.pts-gain .p{font-size:18px}
.result-badge{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:11px;background:var(--surface-2);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:15px;padding:12px 15px;margin-bottom:22px;text-align:left}
.result-badge .e{font-size:28px;flex:none}
.result-badge .x .n{font-size:13px;font-weight:800}
.result-badge .x .d{font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-soft);font-weight:500;margin-top:2px}
.btn-done{width:100%;height:50px;border-radius:15px;background:var(--ink);color:#fff;font-weight:800;font-size:14px}
.btn-done:hover{background:#3D332A}
.btn-ghost{width:100%;height:44px;border-radius:14px;background:transparent;color:var(--ink-soft);font-weight:700;font-size:13px;margin-top:8px}
.btn-ghost:hover{background:var(--surface-2);color:var(--ink)}
.sent-note{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:11px;background:var(--surface-2);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:15px;padding:13px 15px;margin-bottom:20px;text-align:left}
.sent-note svg{width:20px;height:20px;flex:none;color:var(--courage);margin-top:1px}
.sent-note b{font-size:12.5px;font-weight:800;color:var(--ink)}
.sent-note span{font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-soft);font-weight:500;line-height:1.5}
.pts-gain .pts-sub{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#C79A4A}
.confetti{position:fixed;width:9px;height:14px;top:-20px;z-index:95;pointer-events:none;border-radius:2px}

/* toast */
.toast{position:fixed;bottom:26px;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,80px);z-index:88;
  background:var(--ink);color:#fff;padding:13px 20px;border-radius:14px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg);transition:.35s cubic-bezier(.2,.9,.3,1.1)}
.toast.show{transform:translate(-50%,0)}
.toast .e{font-size:17px}

@media(max-width:1080px){.discover{grid-template-columns:1fr}.rail{display:none}.sched-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
.fade{animation:fade .4s ease}
@keyframes fade{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px)}to{opacity:1;transform:none}}

/* ===================== LANDING ===================== */
.landing{position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:120;overflow-y:auto;
  background:
    radial-gradient(1100px 600px at 12% -12%, #FFE3D6 0%, transparent 55%),
    radial-gradient(900px 560px at 102% -4%, #FCEBC8 0%, transparent 52%),
    linear-gradient(162deg,#FBF1E8,#F6E7DA);
  -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}
.landing.hide{display:none}
.l-wrap{max-width:760px;margin:0 auto;padding:54px 28px 60px;text-align:center}
.l-badge{display:inline-block;font-size:12px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.02em;color:var(--brand-deep);background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--brand-soft);padding:7px 15px;border-radius:30px;box-shadow:var(--shadow)}
.l-logo{width:74px;height:74px;border-radius:22px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--brand),#F2935F);display:grid;place-items:center;margin:26px auto 18px;box-shadow:0 14px 32px rgba(238,88,54,.32)}
.l-logo svg{width:38px;height:38px}
.l-title{font-size:38px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.02em;color:var(--ink)}
.l-tag{font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;color:var(--ink-soft);font-weight:500;margin:14px auto 0;max-width:560px}
.l-tag b{color:var(--brand-deep);font-weight:800}
.l-cta{display:flex;gap:12px;justify-content:center;margin-top:30px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.l-cta button{height:54px;padding:0 32px;border-radius:15px;background:var(--brand);color:#fff;font-weight:800;font-size:16px;border:none;cursor:pointer;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(238,88,54,.28);transition:.15s;font-family:inherit}
.l-cta button:hover{background:var(--brand-deep);transform:translateY(-1px)}
.l-card{background:rgba(255,255,255,.74);backdrop-filter:blur(6px);border:1px solid #fff;border-radius:24px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);padding:28px 30px;margin-top:38px;text-align:left}
.l-card h2{font-size:13px;font-weight:800;color:var(--brand-deep);letter-spacing:.03em;margin-bottom:12px}
.l-why p{font-size:15px;line-height:1.85;color:var(--ink);font-weight:500}
.l-why p b{color:var(--brand-deep);font-weight:800}
.l-feats{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:14px;margin-top:16px}
.l-feat{background:rgba(255,255,255,.74);border:1px solid #fff;border-radius:20px;padding:22px 18px;text-align:center;box-shadow:var(--shadow)}
.l-feat .e{font-size:26px}
.l-feat .t{font-size:14.5px;font-weight:800;margin-top:10px;color:var(--ink)}
.l-feat .d{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-top:6px;line-height:1.55}
.l-goals{list-style:none;margin-top:6px;display:grid;gap:11px;padding:0}
.l-goals li{display:flex;gap:11px;align-items:flex-start;font-size:14.5px;color:var(--ink);font-weight:600;line-height:1.5}
.l-goals .ck{width:22px;height:22px;border-radius:7px;background:var(--go-soft);color:var(--go);display:grid;place-items:center;flex:none;font-size:12px;font-weight:900;margin-top:1px}
.l-foot{margin-top:34px;font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-faint);font-weight:600}
.l-foot .pwc{font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-weight:800;color:#5A554F}
@media(max-width:560px){.l-title{font-size:30px}.l-tag{font-size:15px}.l-feats{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<!-- ===================== LANDING (첫 화면) ===================== -->
<div class="landing" id="landing">
  <div class="l-wrap">
    <div class="l-badge">삼일PwC · 신규 입사자 Pre-boarding 미션</div>
    <div class="l-logo"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M5 8h11a3 3 0 0 1 0 6h-1M5 8v6a4 4 0 0 0 4 4h3a4 4 0 0 0 4-4M5 8V7M8 4.5c0 1-1 1-1 2M11 4.5c0 1-1 1-1 2" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div>
    <h1 class="l-title">삼일 커피챗 챌린지</h1>
    <p class="l-tag">합격하고 입사하기 전, 가장 설레지만 막막한 그 시기.<br>선배와의 커피챗 한 잔으로 <b>미리 연결되는</b> 신규 입사자 네트워킹 챌린지예요.</p>
    <div class="l-cta"><button onclick="enterApp()">시작하기 →</button></div>

    <div class="l-card l-why">
      <h2>💡 왜 만들었나요</h2>
      <p>합격 후 입사 전 공백기에 신규 입사자들은 <b>막연한 불안과 단절감</b>을 느낍니다. ‘삼일 커피챗 챌린지’는 이 시기를 <b>선배와의 가벼운 커피챗</b>으로 채워, 입사 전부터 자연스러운 <b>네트워킹과 소속감</b>을 만들도록 설계했어요. 거절조차 ‘용기 점수’가 되는 게이미피케이션으로, 결과보다 <b>한 발 내딛는 시도</b> 자체를 응원합니다.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="l-feats">
      <div class="l-feat"><div class="e">🔍</div><div class="t">멘토 카드 탐색</div><div class="d">소개팅형 프로필 카드로 결이 맞는 선배 발견</div></div>
      <div class="l-feat"><div class="e">⚡</div><div class="t">용기 점수 시스템</div><div class="d">신청·성사·거절 모두 점수 — 시도가 곧 보상</div></div>
      <div class="l-feat"><div class="e">🤖</div><div class="t">AI 주제 추천</div><div class="d">어색하지 않은 첫 대화 질문을 자동 제안</div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="l-foot"><span class="pwc">pwc</span></div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="app">
  <!-- SIDEBAR -->
  <aside class="side">
    <div class="brand">
      <div class="brand-mark">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M5 8h11a3 3 0 0 1 0 6h-1M5 8v6a4 4 0 0 0 4 4h3a4 4 0 0 0 4-4M5 8V7M8 4.5c0 1-1 1-1 2M11 4.5c0 1-1 1-1 2" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="brand-name">삼일 커피챗<small>SAMIL COFFEE·CHAT</small></div>
    </div>

    <nav class="nav" id="nav">
      <div class="nav-label">메뉴</div>
      <button class="nav-item on" data-v="discover">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><rect x="4" y="5" width="16" height="14" rx="3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7"/><path d="M4 9h16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7"/><circle cx="9" cy="14" r="1.5" fill="currentColor"/></svg>
        신청하기
      </button>
      <button class="nav-item" data-v="schedule">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><rect x="4" y="5" width="16" height="15" rx="3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7"/><path d="M4 9h16M8 3v4M16 3v4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        내 일정 <span class="badge">2</span>
      </button>
      <button class="nav-item" data-v="network">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><circle cx="6" cy="7" r="2.4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7"/><circle cx="18" cy="7" r="2.4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7"/><circle cx="12" cy="17" r="2.4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7"/><path d="M8 8.5l3 6.5M16 8.5l-3 6.5M8 7h8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7"/></svg>
        네트워크 맵
      </button>
      <button class="nav-item" data-v="leaderboard">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M7 20h10M9 20v-3m6 3v-3M6 4h12v4a6 6 0 0 1-12 0V4Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><path d="M6 6H4v1a3 3 0 0 0 2 2.8M18 6h2v1a3 3 0 0 1-2 2.8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        리더보드
      </button>
    </nav>

    <div class="side-foot">
      <div class="courage-card">
        <div class="courage-top">
          <div class="courage-lab">⚡ 용기 게이지</div>
          <div class="courage-lvl" id="lvlTag">Lv.3</div>
        </div>
        <div class="courage-pts" id="cPts">65<span>pts</span></div>
        <div class="gauge"><div class="gauge-fill" id="cGauge" style="width:65%"></div></div>
        <div class="courage-next" id="cNext">레벨 4까지 35 pts · 거절 1회</div>
      </div>
      <button class="reset-btn" onclick="logout()" title="로그아웃">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M15 12H4m0 0 3.5-3.5M4 12l3.5 3.5M10 7V5.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 11.5 4h6A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 19 5.5v13a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5h-6A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 10 18.5V17" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        로그아웃
      </button>
      <div class="save-hint">☁️ 서버 DB에 저장 · 어느 기기에서 열어도 이어집니다</div>
    </div>
  </aside>

  <!-- MAIN -->
  <main class="main">
    <div class="topbar">
      <div>
        <h1 id="tbTitle">오늘의 추천 선배</h1>
        <div class="sub" id="tbSub">AI가 나와 결이 맞는 선배를 골라드려요</div>
      </div>
      <div class="topbar-right">
        <button class="bell" id="bell" onclick="toggleNotif()" aria-label="알림">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6 9a6 6 0 1 1 12 0c0 4 1.2 5.5 2 6.3.4.4.1 1.2-.5 1.2H4.5c-.6 0-.9-.8-.5-1.2.8-.8 2-2.3 2-6.3Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linejoin="round"/><path d="M9.5 19a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 5 0" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
          <span class="bell-dot" id="bellDot" hidden></span>
        </button>
        <div class="me">
          <div class="me-txt" style="text-align:right" id="meTxt">—<small id="meSub"></small></div>
          <div class="me-av" id="meAv">나</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- notification panel -->
      <div class="notif-panel" id="notifPanel" hidden>
        <div class="notif-head">알림 <button onclick="markAllRead()">모두 읽음</button></div>
        <div id="notifList"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="view" id="view"></div>
  </main>
</div>

<!-- result modal -->
<div class="scrim" id="scrim">
  <div class="result" id="result"></div>
</div>
<div class="toast" id="toast"><span class="e">⚡</span><span id="toastTxt"></span></div>

<!-- login gate -->
<div class="login-scrim" id="login">
  <div class="login-card">
    <div class="login-brand">
      <div class="brand-mark" style="width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:13px">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M5 8h11a3 3 0 0 1 0 6h-1M5 8v6a4 4 0 0 0 4 4h3a4 4 0 0 0 4-4M5 8V7M8 4.5c0 1-1 1-1 2M11 4.5c0 1-1 1-1 2" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div><div class="lb-t">삼일 커피챗 챌린지</div><div class="lb-s">신규 입사자 네트워킹</div></div>
    </div>
    <p class="login-lead">입사 전 선배들과 커피챗으로 연결되는 동기 네트워킹 챌린지예요. 이름과 회사 이메일로 시작하세요.</p>
    <label class="fld"><span>이름</span><input id="inName" placeholder="예) 김신입"></label>
    <label class="fld"><span>회사 이메일</span><input id="inEmail" type="email" placeholder="예) sinip.kim@samil.example.com"></label>
    <div class="fld-row">
      <label class="fld"><span>입사 기수</span>
        <select id="inCohort"><option>36기</option><option>37기</option></select></label>
      <label class="fld"><span>희망/배정 본부</span>
        <select id="inDept"><option>Audit</option><option>Tax</option><option>Deals</option><option>Consulting</option><option>People &amp; L&amp;D</option></select></label>
    </div>
    <button class="login-btn" id="loginBtn" onclick="doLogin()">시작하기 →</button>
    <div class="login-err" id="loginErr"></div>
    <div class="login-foot">인사팀이신가요? <a href="/admin">HR 대시보드 →</a></div>
  </div>
</div>

<script src="app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
